							Maintenance Guide
						</a>
						<a href="#pricing" class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 focus:bg-green-600 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 focus:ring-offset-2 text-white font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-full transition-colors" role="menuitem" aria-label="Buy Now - Go to pricing">
