						<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Expert Septic System Resources</h2>
						<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
							Learn from the professionals. Our comprehensive guides help you understand, maintain, and protect your septic investment.
						</p>
						
						<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-6">
							<a href="/septic-tank-maintenance-guide/" class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow group">
